column5: Sign Man charters made a first time muskie angler pretty happy    Beautiful big monster fish
He seems to have lost a little weight. The fish didn't lose anything though. It was doing the rounds yesterday. A magnificent specimen indeed!
I agree.  Congrats to the angler on that one.  That would put a huge smile on anyone's face.
first fish for that guy? poor son of a gun is now in for a life of dissapointment if he keeps on fishing...I'm sooo glad all my fish are puny so I have something to beat
the poor guy is probably STILL shaking,what a rush to that fight must have been to boat that big girl  vance
What no weight for us to fight about? very nice fish good job.   Art
Wow, a catch of a lifetime!!!  Congrats to him.  I can only dream I'll catch one that big some day
Wow..  I'll have to show that to the boys at work tomorrow.  Nice fish..
Wow! I don't know what else to say.
What a tank!!! That is just sick. That's an incredible fish for anyone let alone a first muskie!
GOing to be hard to beat that... First fish = biggest lol
What an incredible fish from possibly best musky waters in world. Must be over 60 lbs.....
HOW MANY NICE FISH DOES IT TAKE TO KEEP THAT GUY ALIVE
Hmmmm.........trying to understand that one too Dax
I think he means all the large fish the 60 inch musky probably ate to get that big.
And suggesting thats somehow not right???
